text: ยง 11-219 Books of annual record; delivery for publication. Within two weeks after the delivery of the assessment-rolls to the council, the commissioner of finance shall furnish to the director of the City Record a copy of the several books of the annual record of the assessed valuation of real estate, omitting, however, the two columns headed respectively "size of house" and "houses on lot."

chapter.text: REAL PROPERTY ASSESSMENT, TAXATION AND CHARGES
